# 📊 FNP Sales Analysis Dashboard (Excel)

This project presents a dynamic **Sales Analysis Dashboard** built using **Microsoft Excel**, analyzing the performance of **Ferns N Petals (FNP)** — a leading brand in gifting and floral services. The dashboard tracks key metrics such as total orders, revenue, product category performance, delivery times, and customer behavior.

---

## 🧠 Key Insights

- 🧾 **Total Orders:** 1000  
- 💰 **Total Revenue:** ₹35,20,984  
- ⏱️ **Average Delivery Time:** 5.53 days  
- 💳 **Avg. Customer Spend:** ₹3,520.98  
- 🗓️ Peak Sales Months: **March** and **September**  
- 🏙️ Top City by Orders: **Dhanbad**  
- 🎁 Best-selling Product: **Magman Set**

---

## 📌 Dashboard Features

- **Revenue Breakdown by:**
  - 🎉 Occasion (Anniversary, Diwali, Valentine’s Day, etc.)
  - 📦 Product Category (Cakes, Mugs, Sweets, etc.)
  - 🗓️ Day of the Week and Month

- **Visuals:**
  - Bar charts, line graphs, slicers
  - Interactive filtering by **Order Date**, **Delivery Time**, and **Occasion**

- **Top 5 Products & Cities** by revenue and order volume

---

